import index from '../cjs/index.js'
const {
  PostgrestClient,
  PostgrestQueryBuilder,
  PostgrestFilterBuilder,
  PostgrestTransformBuilder,
  PostgrestBuilder,
  PostgrestError,
} = index

export {
  PostgrestBuilder,
  PostgrestClient,
  PostgrestFilterBuilder,
  PostgrestQueryBuilder,
  PostgrestTransformBuilder,
  PostgrestError,
}

// compatibility with CJS output
export default {
  PostgrestClient,
  PostgrestQueryBuilder,
  PostgrestFilterBuilder,
  PostgrestTransformBuilder,
  PostgrestBuilder,
  PostgrestError,
}
